# Service Handler Files

Read the **Handler Pattern** section of `docs/ai/cap-coding-standards.md`.

## Rules

- Extend `cds.ApplicationService`, call `return super.init()` at the end
- **No business logic here** -- only `this.on()`, `this.before()`, `this.after()` registrations
- Delegate to logic modules: `require('./code/entity-on-action-logic')`
- One handler file per service, matching the `.cds` filename
